        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Good things are happening! The Colorado legislature banned dangerous so-called “forever chemicals” used in fossil fuel mining, Starbucks workers in thirteen states voted to unionize, the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau is cracking down on employers that put their workers in debt, New York’s legislature finally reined in crypto mining, and socialists in France are on the cusp of a big comeback.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
